  m_text: '4. Step-by-step: Vertex shaders



    We will now construct a shader
    which operates on the geometry layer of the object, i.e., a vertex shader. In
    dynamic environments such as Unity, we can also use them to model simple animations.


    Open
    Assets > Shaders > AnimatedFlag. To try the shader, create a Material from it
    and drag it onto the Plane on the right.


'
