  m_text: "7. Material masking\n\n\nIt's often useful to mix multiple materials on
    a single object via masking, in order to create compositional visual effects.
    Open Assets > Shader > HeightMask. \n\nOnce you're done, create the material
    as usual and try it on the sphere on the right. After selecting the material
    in the Project view, try and modify its parameters from the Inspector, and see
    how the material reacts!"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
