  m_text: "2. Your first shader\n\n\nGo to Assets > Shaders > YourFirstShader and
    open the asset.\n\nOnce you have completed the shader, go to the Project view
    (below), and select the ShaderGraph object we edited (Assets > Shaders > YourFirstShader).
    Now, right click on it and Create > Material. \n\nSelect the created material
    and drag it on the sphere on the right. Finally, select the sphere: in the Inspector,
    bottom right, you will find the shader information and the parameters we defined
    in the graph. Change the values of \"Color\" to see how the object changes.\n"
